          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1719400302293-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>sea bass fillet[s] </strong>dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>cornflour</strong> all over and rub it into both sides of the fish until fully coated, then set aside for later – this is your <strong>coated sea bass</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1719400307905-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1719400307905-x400.jpg",
