          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1719400307905-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated sea bass fillet[s]</strong>, skin side down, and cook for 5 min, then turn and cook for 1 min further until cooked through – this is your <strong>crispy sea bass</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1719400313325-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1719400313325-x400.jpg",
