            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1719400313325-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy sea bass </strong>with the <strong>sticky rice</strong> (discard the lemongrass!) and <strong>soy greens</strong> to the side</p><p>Spoon over the <strong>pla rad prik sauce</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> sliced spring onion</strong> and your<strong> crispy onions</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
